==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Averroist
<hw>A*ver"ro*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of a sect of peripatetic
philosophers, who appeared in Italy before the restoration of learning;
so denominated from Averroes, or Averrhoes, a celebrated Arabian
philosopher. He held the doctrine of monopsychism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Averruncate</ent>⟦br⟧
